                    You are working in an isolated git worktree:\n\
                    - Worktree: {}\n\
                    - Path: {}\n\
                    - Branch: {}\n\n",
                    active_wt.worktree_name,
                    active_wt.worktree_path.display(),
                    active_wt.worktree_name
                ));
